PrecisOrder which provides authority (a) for the National Capital Commission to grant a seventy-five year Easement (ES-720-2) to Ontario Hydro for the installation, operation, etc., of two 500 kV electrical power transmission lines across a four kilometre strip of Greenbelt land situate south of Knoxdale Road, starting at the municipal border between the Cities of Kanata and Nepean to a point on Cedarview Road in Nepean, Ontario; and (b) for the revocation of Order in Council P.C. 1988-2/916 of May 12, 1988.
